                            <h3 style="padding-top: 10px;">Passwords:</h3>
                            <p>The personal data record created through your registration with our Web site can only be accessed with the unique password associated with that record. To protect the integrity of the information contained in this record, you should not disclose or otherwise reveal your password to third parties.</p>
                           
